1. *Pljačka* je bila vrlo brutalna. (The robbery was very brutal.)
2. Ova *pljačka* se desila pre nedelju dana. (This robbery happened a week ago.)
3. On je osuđen zbog *pljačke* banke. (He was convicted for a bank robbery.)
4. Policija je uhapsila dvojicu osumnjičenih za *pljačku*. (The police arrested two suspects for the robbery.)
5. Oni su izvršili *pljačku* prodavnice noću. (They committed a store robbery at night.)
6. Bio je očev svjedok kad se desila *pljačka*. (He was his father's witness when the robbery occurred.)
7. *Pljačka* je uzrokovala veliku štetu u banci. (The robbery caused a lot of damage to the bank.)
8. Ona je videla počinioce *pljačke* i pozvala policiju. (She saw the perpetrators of the robbery and called the police.)
9. Posle *pljačke* se osećam nesigurno u gradu. (After the robbery, I feel insecure in the city.)
10. Osuđenik je u zatvoru zbog *pljačke*. (The convict is in prison for the robbery.)